    <eval phase="Final" priority="50000"><![CDATA[
      ~ Lets add to our modified Ice Storm spell information for reference
      #appenddesc[spIceSto3, "{b}Three times per day{/b}, the wearer of the crown can call down a storm of razor sharp bone  shards.Similar to {i}ice storm{/i} with the following differences.{BR}These shards deal 5d6 points of slashing damage to all creatures in a 10-foot-radius burst and each creature bleeds on its turn for an additional 1d6 points of damage (this bleed can be healed or stopped as normal).{BR}Creatures in the area can attempt a DC 16 Reflex save to halve the damage and negate the bleed."]]]></eval>
