  <thing id="ir3PMFSRoL" name="Ring of Light" description="This ring is made from pale, white gold set with a trio of small diamonds on its face. \n\nThe ring can shed light, as per the spell, on command. \n\nIn addition, three times per day as a standard action, the wielder can attempt a melee touch attack against an undead creature to deal 1d8+5 points of damage, as if using cure light wounds. \n\nThis cannot be used to heal a living creature. The undead creature receives a DC 11 Will save for half damage.\n\n{b}CONSTRUCTION{/b} Forge Ring, {i}cure light wounds{/i}, {i}light{/i}; Cost 2,000 gp" compset="Ring">
